PropertySetDef.Name: Pset_CommunicationsApplianceTypeOpticalLineTerminal
PropertySetDef.Definition: Properties common to a optical line terminal. This property set is applied to a type or occurrence of _IfcCommunicationsAppliance_ with predefined type OPTICALLINETERMINAL.

PropertyDef.Name: NumberOfSlots
PropertyDef.Definition: Indicates the number of device slots.

PropertyDef.Name: NumberOfInterfaces
PropertyDef.Definition: Indicates the types of interfaces and their number in the device.
